SliTaz forge
===============================================================================

This repos provide all files, theme and custom packages used by SliTaz network.

 * doc:    Use Dokuwiki
 * forum:  Use Vanilla
 * labs:   Use Redmine
 * people: Own php/html code


To update or fix theme, please test it well before, commit and then notice
<pankso at slitaz.org> who will update modified theme.

Note that ‡aAll receipts was made for tazwok 3.1 and SliTaz 3.0.
To update or fix packages do the same as for themes and notice <erjo at slitaz.org>.
